    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing... there is no new foundation. the foundation is me. everything i build is made of the same broken parts. it feels less like a \"pattern\" and more like a law of physics. no matter how much i try to change, the result is always the same. it's just constant, repetitive failure. it's like i'm stuck in a loop that can't be fixed, just repeated.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
